text: Eunidia caffra is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Fahraeus in 1872.BioLib.cz - Eunidia caffra. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==Subspecies== * Eunidia caffra caffra Fahraeus, 1872 * Eunidia caffra socia Gahan, 1909 ==References== Category:Eunidiini Category:Beetles described in 1872
